    • match

      public int match(JFlowKey key)
      Compares the flow keys and returns the direction in which the match occured. Forward or reverse.
      Parameters:
      key - key to compare against this key
      Returns:
      0 means key's don't match, 1 keys matched in forward direction and -1 means matched in reverse direction.
